{"tid":107724,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人控制唔到情緒？","createTime":"2017-02-04T16:02:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-04T17:02:39.000Z","uid":36674,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"43ed701df693d6fdf3fa136d210f1411dd1fafa1","tid":107724,"uid":36674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:02:19.000Z","msg":"會無啦啦喊，好失落，咩都唔想做<br />\n好容易嬲同失控<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n心入面成日自責，覺得今日搞成咁都係我自己問題<br />\n成日有把聲係到踩自己<br />\n好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實係咪應該睇醫生？"},{"pid":"f1bcb509cba39f014439abc778276acb79080710","tid":107724,"uid":1436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:03:55.000Z","msg":"絕對要！"},{"pid":"301938ba25e03ae47777803206826374cc31c35f","tid":107724,"uid":82258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:12:30.000Z","msg":"老柒講，你最好搵野做下，例如做運動，sit up又好，乜都好，增加多巴胺，令都個人開心的，出去吸多的新鮮空氣，飲多的水同食生果都有幫助。一個禮拜過去，仲係咁，你可能患上抑鬱症"},{"pid":"3b1da24dc69de20950bf6b72f4f63bef02cd6d9e","tid":107724,"uid":54015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:21:04.000Z","msg":"抑鬱症<br />\n<br />\n聽到聲可能係嚴重嗰隻<br />\n<br />\n快啲睇醫生"},{"pid":"401b65c20bf7cbb29429cbda8972a1ebd9a0bd66","tid":107724,"uid":36674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:22:49.000Z","msg":"多謝樓上的巴打們<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實我都有做下運動，但內心總係好似有嘢un住，<br />\n做完都係好沮喪好易喊<br />\n打算同男朋友講分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為覺得自己係到害緊人，<br />\n成日好易失控，上一秒笑下一秒喊，再下一秒就發脾氣，佢同我講「對住你，唔知我做咩先叫啱」<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我好想控制到自己，但一嬲就好似點著咗咁<br />\n覺得自己好無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54e374e1ca39aa64ace767a5904fb0b6dafb8553","tid":107724,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:35:55.000Z","msg":"成日一嬲就失晒理智，一醒返就發現打爛好多野，衫都爛撚埋，得返條褲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bd2dc189128050ba638633fd576dbd787025e3e","tid":107724,"uid":81222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:40:42.000Z","msg":"有無諗過咩原因令到你咁？<br />\n例如 工作學業感情個啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申 我有時都會"},{"pid":"01cce04d73668da77cfb6ba4fa85926cb4000461","tid":107724,"uid":35324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:41:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3de3d400e0eaf9f5646b789bf567b5437fae54bf","tid":107724,"uid":36674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:44:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成日一嬲就失晒理智，一醒返就發現打爛好多野，衫都爛撚埋，得返條褲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔記得發生過咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5971d380b216f1fbab06a6eaf3aaf2383d99de45","tid":107724,"uid":36674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:49:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無諗過咩原因令到你咁？<br />\n例如 工作學業感情個啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申 我有時都會</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n從小身體都唔好，有d小毛病咁，人地睇覺得無咩大不了，不過對我黎講係一種折磨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到而家都食緊西藥，可能因為咁，由細到大生活都唔太開心<br />\n你係因為咩原因呀？"},{"pid":"5b6b94c6610903892a4f32f2ac45b89707d31625","tid":107724,"uid":36674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:50:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f580462e2107599327ed5ada4d5b4ea08c8fdf8d","tid":107724,"uid":9681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:59:29.000Z","msg":"bio 人可唔可以解釋吓"},{"pid":"b95ece1d19591dcceffbd94e7d2e815df7d3e21e","tid":107724,"uid":81222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T17:02:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有無諗過咩原因令到你咁？<br />\n例如 工作學業感情個啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申 我有時都會</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n從小身體都唔好，有d小毛病咁，人地睇覺得無咩大不了，不過對我黎講係一種折磨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到而家都食緊西藥，可能因為咁，由細到大生活都唔太開心<br />\n你係因為咩原因呀？</blockquote><br />\nHmm都係因為感情同學業<br />\n自己無咩興趣又無依靠 個人成日好頹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我依排都病緊 不停食西葯 食到個人溫溫登登其實真係好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無話可以睇中醫 調理下個身體？<br />\n利申未睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}